lore: The young of the Mindwurm are deceptively powerful, despite their small size. Using their telekinetic powers, they carve tunnels through the earth, saving their sharp fangs for when it's time to take down their enemies. Before gaining too much mass, they can soar through the air with ease, hunting from both above and below.
